    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_008_000008",
    "sentence": "問之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_008_000009",
    "sentence": "對曰：「旦寒甚，俟朝食而後閱，故後。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_008_000010",
    "sentence": "又命分閱章奏，獨取切軍民利病者白之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_008_000011",
    "sentence": "或文字謬誤，不以聞。",
